\end{itemize}

\section*{Differences}
Despite the similarities, there are key differences in teaching methodologies between virtual and conventional classrooms:

\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Environment:} Conventional classrooms are physical, while virtual classrooms are digital.
    \item \textbf{Interaction:} In conventional classrooms, students and teachers interact face-to-face, whereas in virtual classrooms, interaction is often mediated through technology.
